{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ec64e110-7106-4340-a102-8708d037cb20","content":"`.testsettings` files are **no longer supported** in modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's the equivalent for your configuration:\n\n**Your `.testsettings` configured:**\n1. **Test timeout** → `[Timeout]` attribute or `<TestTimeout>` in `.runsettings`\n2. **Assembly resolution** → no longer needed (modern test host handles this)\n3. **Code coverage** → `<DataCollector>` in `.runsettings`\n\nLet me create the replacement:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01QVqiLssoW9pSfq1TTMZbz9","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01GUnbxZuond1RDKgfoj4L35","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-298f511d90ad492ba808a4522310a547/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Replaces the TestTimeout property from .testsettings (value in ms) -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    <!-- AssemblyResolution/DeploymentEnabled is no longer needed in modern MSTest -->\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-298f511d90ad492ba808a4522310a547/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"69ce25fa-134b-4a52-8a3e-00348dcb11eb","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution / test deployment settings\n2. Test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. Code coverage data collector\n\nThey ne